Pre-Game Insights: South Africa have a formidable squad on paper but they have been surprised once by the Netherlands before.
In the T20 World Cup 2022, the Netherlands caused a significant upset by defeating South Africa by 13 runs, which cost the Proteas a spot in the semi-finals.
South Africa’s recent victory against Sri Lanka showcased their formidable bowling attack with Anrich Nortje’s standout performance of 4 wickets for just 7 runs.
The pitch at Nassau Cricket Stadium has been criticized for its inconsistent bounce, which led to injuries for Rohit Sharma and Rishabh Pant during India’s match against Ireland.
The pitch is expected to benefit the bowlers, suggesting another low-scoring contest.
The maximum temperature is expected to be around 19°C with a slight chance of rainfall in prediction.
